19\. It moreover is recorded, in the world.

Sm*ri*ti, moreover, states that the bodies of some specially meritorious
persons, such as Draupadî, Dh*ri*sh*t*adyumna and others, were formed
independently of the fifth oblation' (i.e. sexual union).

